snippet.title: Corsairs Legacy - Official In-Engine Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1594880/Corsairs_Legacy_Pirate_Action_RPG/

Official website: https://corsairslegacy.com/

Today we would like to present you a project that will let fans of Sea Dogs play absolutely new and modern game, the goal of which is to continue the legendary series about pirates.
